body:
### Issue Description

Im running TFTP in a rootless container. 

```podman run -it <image> -p 1093:69/udp```

Will yield a pasta process with a -u flag for the port. 

However, when i start the same container as a quadlet with a PublishPort=1093:69 argument, there is no pasta process with a -u flag and connectivity is broken. 

```
# # Podman podman-units/rootless/pxe-tftpd.container generated by podman_tool.cue::mkunit
[Container]
Label=purpose="Serve NBP (pxelinux), and its config, to PXE firmwares"
Label=app="pxe"
Network=pxe.network
PublishPort=1093:69/udp
PodmanArgs=--publish 1093:69/udp
Image=registry.infrastructure.oruoru.nz:5000/pxe/tftpd
HostName=pxe-tftpd
[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target default.target
[Service]
Restart=always
```

